&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/INDIA-MUMBAI-DAKSHIN-COASTAL-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4609&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/INDIA-MUMBAI-DAKSHIN-COASTAL-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;INDIA- MUMBAI- DAKSHIN COASTAL- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;149&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In a setting inspired by the temples of southern India with Carnatic music to set the mood, Dakshin Coastal specializes in cuisine of the south focusing on seafood and vegetarian dishes and including meat and poultry dishes as well. Winner of the &lt;strong&gt;2014 Times Food Guide award for &ldquo;The Best South Indian Restaurant&amp;#8221;&lt;/strong&gt;. Smart casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contact the restaurant by phone at (91) (22) 2830 3030 or email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:restaurantreservation.itcmaratha@itchotels.in&quot;&gt;restaurantreservation.itcmaratha@itchotels.in&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please provide a cell phone number or local (hotel) contact number in Mumbai. The restaurant will call you on the dining date to reconfirm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

